    • Field Detail

      • subThoroughfare

        public final java.lang.String subThoroughfare
        Sub-thoroughfare (street number) name of the street address or null if not available.

      • thoroughfare

        public final java.lang.String thoroughfare
        The thoroughfare (street name) of the street address or null if not available. For example, for "34 Farnsworth Street" the thoroughfare is "Farnsworth Street".

        In some cases where the sub-thoroughfare is not available the thoroughfare may include the full street address including the street number and street name. For example, "34 Farnsworth Street".
